lead_paragraph: Ellen Port moved into position for her third U.S. Senior Women's Amateur title and seventh USGA championship, winning two matches Wednesday on her 55th birthday — and 32nd anniversary of her father's death — to reach the final.

headline.print_headline: Port, Kraus Reach US Senior Women's Amateur Final
